    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">Index XXIV.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index XV.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Index XXIIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index <app>
                                <lem wit="#L1">XXIIII.</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L2">XXIV.</rdg>
                            </app>, in quo administratio Ioannis Corvini explicatur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXIII. de Ioanne Corvino regni Hungariae
                            gubernatore eiusque fortiter et prudenter gestis</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Erat per id temporis Vladislaus Alberti filius annos natus quinque,
                    idcirco cum per aetatem non esset idoneus, cui regni traderetur administratio,
                    habita ratione <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">gestarum rerum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">rerum gestarum</rdg>
                    </app> aliarumque multarum virtutum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">spectatae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1">spectate</rdg>
                    </app> praesertim multis in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">rebus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">locis</rdg>
                    </app> fidei Ioannis Corvini magno totius Hungariae consensu delectus ipse est,
                    qui regis loco <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">vaivodae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">vaivode</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">vayvodae</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">tamen</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">tantum</rdg>
                    </app> appellatione universum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">regnum cum imperio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">cum imperio regnum</rdg>
                    </app> moderaretur, ipsumque sua illa animi magnitudine illaque in rebus
                    gerendis ei arridente fortuna tutaretur.</s>
                <s n="2">Eam electionem secutus est omnium populorum mirus applausus gaudiumque non
                    mediocre et laetitia incredibilis, tanta <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> erat virtutis viri apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">omnes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">omnis</rdg>
                    </app> Hungaros existimatio.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1–2 = Th 4.44. –
                        Annus electionis Ioannis Hunyadi in gubernatorem regni 1446 fuit; Thuróczy
                        annum 1445 scribit.</note></s>
                <s n="3">Is ante omnia, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> sunt ei visa factu necessaria, curavit, ut corona una et Vladislaus puer
                    Alberti olim regis filius, quem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Fredericus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Fridericus</rdg>
                    </app> augustus apud se tenebat <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(ut ante dictum est)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ut ante dictum est</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">recuperarentur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">recuperaretur</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="4">Sed cum ille restituere recusaret, quod iure postulabatur, indignitatis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">rei</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app> Ioannes impatiens infestis armis excurrit per multa loca, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tenebantur illius ditione, per <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Carintiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Carinthiam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Charinthiam</rdg>
                    </app> praesertim et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Carneolam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Carniolam</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S3 #M">Stiriamque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2">Styriamque</rdg>
                    </app>, et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeterquam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">preterquam</rdg>
                    </app> quod multarum civitatum atque villarum agros incendiis ferroque vastavit,
                    ingentem etiam inde <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praedam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">predam</rdg>
                    </app> pecorum atque hominum traxit.</s>
                <s n="5">Fecit id vir prudentissimus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">eo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app> consilio, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Fredericus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Fridericus</rdg>
                    </app> ob <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">acceptum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">accaeptum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">receptum</rdg>
                    </app> tam grande <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">detrimentum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">receptum</rdg>
                    </app> ad restituendum Hungaris, quod suum erat, adduceretur, sed ille parum id
                    curavit, perinde atque ad rem suam nihil attineret.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">3–5 = Th 4.45. – 3 <hi rend="italic">ut ante dictum est</hi>
                        cf. Index XIII.13.</note></s>
                <s n="6">Fuere ea tempestate permulti mortales, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Fredericum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Fridericum</rdg>
                    </app> accusarent <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #L2">et ignaviae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ignaviae</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">desidiaeque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">desidieque</rdg>
                    </app> propterea, quod cum illi non deessent opes, quibus potuisset repugnare
                    hosti, se tamen domi continuit, et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">violentiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">violentiae<add type="insert"> non
                                restitit</add></rdg>
                    </app>, quia cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">esset</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">cẽt</rdg>
                    </app> princeps Christianus, quod sciebat non esse suum, sibi retinuerit tam
                    obstinata <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">pertinacia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #S2">pertinatia</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">6 = ?</note></s>
                <s n="7">Movit et bellum Ioannes, quod ad extremum confecit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">feliciter</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #R">foeliciter</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">faeliciter</rdg>
                    </app>, adversus Georgium <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Serviae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Servie</rdg>
                    </app> despotum, a quo fuerat magna et indigna et, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> non <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">erat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2">erant</rdg>
                    </app> aequo animo ferenda, lacessitus iniuria.</s>
                <s n="8">Confecto <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> bello, quod ei fuerat cum Turcis, rediens per Serviam in Hungariam
                    diversatus est apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ipsum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2"/>
                    </app> Georgium, a quo credebat amice se <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R">hospicio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">hospitio</rdg>
                    </app> suscipiendum.</s>
                <s n="9">At vero ille <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">hospitii</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S2">hospicii</rdg>
                    </app> iure violato non amicum sed hostem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">se Ioanni</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ioanni se</rdg>
                    </app> exhibuit, captum enim <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ipsum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">ipsum<note type="critic">P addit et del.
                                    litteras:</note><del><add type="insert">in</add></del></rdg>
                    </app> carcere <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L2">asservavit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">observavit</rdg>
                    </app>, nec inde abire permissus esset, nisi Ladislaum filium obsidem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">apud</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">aqud</rdg>
                    </app> illum reliquisset.</s>
                <s n="10"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Susceptis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Suscaeptis</rdg>
                    </app> tamen armis adversus illum haud multo post profectus, cum multum agrorum
                    una prope excursione per Rasciam pervastasset<app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">, compulit illum, ut obsidem restitueret</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">7–10 = Th 4.47.</note></s>
                <s n="11"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Suscepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Suscaepit</rdg>
                    </app> et expeditionem contra Bohemos, qui suis egressi finibus aliquot
                    Hungarorum castella expugnaverant, ipse vero non modo occupata recuperavit, sed
                    et profligato hostium exercitu multa castella multumque agrorum illis ademit,
                    post haec multa paravit in eius nationis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">exitium</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2">exitum</rdg>
                    </app>, quae plane confecisset <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">felicissime</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #R">foelicissime</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">faelicissime</rdg>
                    </app>, nisi eius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S1 #S2 #M">coeptis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #Z #L1 #R #L2">caeptis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">ceptis</rdg>
                    </app> fuissent impedimento nonnullorum ex Hungarica nobilitate in ipsius caput
                    paratae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">proditorum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app> insidiae, itaque adactus est necessitate, ut, quae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"><app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">conceperat</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">concaeperat</rdg>
                            </app> animo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">animo conceperant</rdg>
                    </app>, in tempus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">differret</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L2">deferret</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">diferret</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2">oportunius</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">opportunius</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">11 = Th 4.48–49.</note></s>
                <s n="12">Deinde cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Amoractus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #R">Amorattus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Amurates</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">Amoratus</rdg>
                    </app> Turcarum imperator pararet invadere Rasciam, ideoque Georgius suis
                    diffidens viribus Ioannis petivisset auxilia, ut licet in ipsum aliquando
                    peccasset, cum tamen esset homo Christianus, non esset a duce Christianissimo in
                    tanta <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">rerum mole</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">mole rerum</rdg>
                    </app> deserendus, non <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abnuit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">abivit</rdg>
                    </app> ipse, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">sed</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sed<add type="insert">
                            et</add></rdg>
                    </app> opem illi tulit et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">in tempore</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">affuit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">afluit</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">adfuit</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="13">Cum suis enim copiis Turcis ivit obviam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">commissaque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">cõmmissaque</rdg>
                    </app> pugna victor evasit, quippe qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">plerosque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">plaerosque</rdg>
                    </app> illorum vertit in fugam, multos occidit, illos autem, qui erant bello
                    meliores, cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #M">Friczebugo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #R">Frizebugo</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Frizebego</rdg>
                    </app> illorum duce captos tradidit Georgio, qui pro sua libidine illos vel
                    trucidaret vel <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coniiceret</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">coiiceret</rdg>
                    </app> in vincula aut traderet suis, a quibus auro redimerentur.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">12–13 = Th 4.50.</note></s>
                <s n="14">Paucis postea interiectis mensibus, cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Fredericus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Fridericus</rdg>
                    </app> caesar ageret in Nova Civitate, quod oppidum in Austria est, nec vellet
                    restituere Vladislaum Hungaris, qui illum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(quod erat eorum rex)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quod erat eorum rex</rdg>
                    </app> poscebant, ab illis Ioannis consilio ac iussione obsessus est,
                    perseveratumque fuit in obsidione, donec affectus ille <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">taedio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #L1">tedio</rdg>
                    </app> regem illis tradidit.</s>
                <s n="15">Cur autem tradere illum ante noluerit, hanc reddebat ipse causam, quod
                    timebat <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">adolescentulo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">adulescentulo</rdg>
                    </app>, ne videlicet, si in manus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">veniret</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">venisset</rdg>
                    </app> Hungarorum, fore fortasse quempiam, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">ad<note type="critic">P insertum</note></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app> illum necandum aliquid pararet insidiarum.</s>
                <s n="16"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> post multa ultro citroque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">dictitata</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">dictata</rdg>
                    </app> res ita composita est, ut Hungari aequo paterentur animo, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ut a</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">vel a</rdg>
                    </app> caesare adhiberetur adolescentulo vir aliquis natione Germanus, qui illi
                    assisteret illumque educaret, donec ad regnum administrandum esset idoneus.</s>
                <s n="17">Ubi inter ipsos ita conventum est, permittente caesare Hungari Vladislaum
                    laeti Viennam honestissima Germanorum nobilium frequentia comitatum
                        deduxere.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">14–17 =Th 4.51.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
